# Defense-in-depth — service-account / credential JSONs should NEVER live in
# the repo (set them via `wrangler secret put` instead), but if one ever
# lands in this dir by accident, git won't track it.
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
*service-account*.json
*serviceAccount*.json
*credentials*.json
gcp-*.json
